        <item>
            <title>1.0.21</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new</h3>
<ul>
<li>Settings → General → Notifications now tells you when macOS has <strong>denied</strong> notification permission, with a one-click button to open the right pane in System Settings (BOX-94).</li>
</ul>]]></description>
