        <item>
            <title>1.0.20</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>Bug fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fixed double-clicking an email in <strong>Trash</strong> opening a popout window with a blank body (only the subject was shown). Trashed messages now render correctly in the popout (BOX-16).</li>
</ul>]]></description>
